snippet: Stephan El Shaarawy ended a three-year drought by scoring the winning goal as Italy beat Azerbaijan, 3-1, Saturday to qualify for next year’s European Championship.
abstract: Honduras men's national team defeats United States, 2-0, in qualifying match for 2016 Olympics; other soccer matches and news noted.
lead_paragraph: Stephan El Shaarawy ended a three-year drought by scoring the winning goal as Italy beat Azerbaijan, 3-1, Saturday to qualify for next year’s European Championship.
